WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.530 --> 00:00:04.800
Xo‘sh, keling, ushbu ikkita qadamdagi 
kodlar nima ekanligini aniqlaylik.

00:00:04.800 --> 00:00:09.040
Shunday qilib, birinchisi, siz "A" jamoasi uchun 
ochko to‘plashingiz va uni o‘zgartirishingiz.

00:00:09.040 --> 00:00:12.100
Va men buni hozircha o‘zgartiraman 
deb aytmoqchiman va

00:00:12.100 --> 00:00:14.560
biz uni bir soniyada nimaga 
o‘zgartirganimizni aniqlaymiz.

00:00:14.560 --> 00:00:16.309
Mana bu o‘zgaruvchiga ega bo‘lasiz.

00:00:16.309 --> 00:00:18.520
Va bu o‘zgaruvchining qiymatini 
o‘zgartirmoqchi bo‘lganingizda, 

00:00:18.520 --> 00:00:21.020
o‘zlashtirish operatoridan foydalanishingiz kerak.

00:00:21.020 --> 00:00:23.260
Va keyin siz uni nimaga 
o‘zgartirayotganingizni aniqlay olasiz.

00:00:24.570 --> 00:00:26.560
Xo‘sh, siz uni 3 ga oshiryapsiz.

00:00:26.560 --> 00:00:31.207
Bu degani, siz hozirda 
"A" guruhidagi barcha qiymatlarni olib, 

00:00:31.207 --> 00:00:32.800
tayinlash operatoridan foydalanishingiz kerak.

00:00:32.800 --> 00:00:34.060
Ya’ni bu ikkalasi o‘xshashdir.

00:00:34.060 --> 00:00:37.400
3 ga orttirish, 
joriy qiymatni olish va 3 ni qo‘shish.

00:00:38.640 --> 00:00:40.710
Shunday qilib, agar biz joriy qiymatni 
olsak va shunchaki o‘zgaruvchining 

00:00:42.530 --> 00:00:44.936
nomini yozib olishimiz mumkin bo‘lsa.

00:00:44.936 --> 00:00:48.585
Qo‘shimcha belgi va 3 bo‘lishi kerak.

00:00:48.585 --> 00:00:52.385
Biz "Score Team A" ning joriy qiymatini 3 ga oshirmoqdamiz.

00:00:52.385 --> 00:00:55.415
Va, albatta, nuqta-vergul bilan yakunlang.

00:00:56.465 --> 00:01:00.630
Men bu yerda int yozmayapman, 
chunki bu o‘zgaruvchi allaqachon e’lon qilingan.

00:01:00.630 --> 00:01:02.550
Biz buni bir necha videodars oldinroq bajargandik.

00:01:02.550 --> 00:01:04.040
Kodni ko‘rib chiqsak, aniqroq bo‘ladi.

00:01:05.160 --> 00:01:07.560
Qanday bo‘lmasin, keyingi qadamni tezroq bajaraylik.

00:01:07.560 --> 00:01:12.280
Ochkoni ko‘rsatish uchun men nusxa ko‘chirgan 
chop etish usulidan foydalanishim kerak.

00:01:12.280 --> 00:01:16.970
Oldin men buni 3 ni namoyish qilishni aytgandim.

00:01:16.970 --> 00:01:19.140
Ammo men 3 raqamini ko‘rsatishni xohlamayman.

00:01:19.140 --> 00:01:22.180
Men Score Team A dagi qiymatni ko‘rsatmoqchiman.

00:01:23.410 --> 00:01:27.290
Men bu yerda qo‘yishim kerak bo‘lgan narsa - A guruhidagi ochkolardir.

00:01:29.340 --> 00:01:33.510
Men qavslarim yoki figurali qavslarni unitib qoldirmayman.

00:01:33.510 --> 00:01:36.930
Yaxshi, buni kodga kiritamiz va hamma 
kod ishlayotganiga ishonch hosil qilamiz.

00:01:36.930 --> 00:01:38.530
Shunday qilib, men Java kodidaman.

00:01:39.910 --> 00:01:44.840
Men ushbu addThreeforTeamA usuliga 
o‘tmoqchiman, 

00:01:44.840 --> 00:01:49.310
chunki bu "+3" tugmachasini bosganimda 
ro‘y beradigan kodlardir.

00:01:49.310 --> 00:01:52.820
Men buni hozir olib tashlamoqchiman, chunki bu eski kod.

00:01:52.820 --> 00:01:54.900
Va men ikkala qadamimni bajaraman.

00:01:54.900 --> 00:01:59.010
Birinchisi scoreTeamA o‘zgaruvchisini olib, 
uni eski qiymatiga 

00:02:00.440 --> 00:02:07.250
ya’ni 3 ga tenglashtirish edi.

00:02:07.250 --> 00:02:09.139
Mayli, bu uch bosqichga ko‘payish.

00:02:09.139 --> 00:02:14.540
Va mana bundan keyin chop etish
ikkinchi qadam edi, 

00:02:14.540 --> 00:02:19.472
ya’ni, Team A ning 
ochko o‘zgaruvchisini nazarda tutdim.

00:02:19.472 --> 00:02:22.800
Mana shu mening ikkita qadamim bor.

00:02:24.650 --> 00:02:27.620
Xo‘sh, endi haqiqat onlari, keling, yana 3 ochkoga bosaylik.

00:02:28.770 --> 00:02:30.225
Yaxshi, u 3 ga oshdi.

00:02:31.520 --> 00:02:38.360
Bu kichikroq, ammo u 6, 9, 12, 15 gacha 
o‘sdi, yaxshi, juda zo‘r.

00:02:38.360 --> 00:02:40.040
Bu ishlayotganga o‘xshayapti.

00:02:40.040 --> 00:02:42.890
Bu boshqa tugmachalar ishlamaydi, 
lekin biz ularning ishlashini kutmagandik ham.

